      <p>I really want to try these with my Thanksgiving dinner, but I am wondering&#8230;could I make them in advance and they still turn out all right. Not days, of course, but a few hours. I&#8217;m just terrified of the timing and last minute rush. In my youth, the famous call after we had already sat down to dinner was, &#8220;Damn! The rolls!&#8221;</p>
